{"tid":1862722,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"呢排又多左五毛開post帶風向","createTime":"2020-02-04T19:04:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-05T08:14:30.000Z","uid":239336,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"946b60d991a8c9758df2a0a093b7794afb9e3261","tid":1862722,"uid":239336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T19:04:31.000Z","msg":"近呢幾日連登多左好多類型既五毛風向post同留言！<br />\n多數內容都係話中國唔會支爆、失敗主義同埋分化post等等，企圖打擊香港人抗爭士氣同令香港人產生無力感，從而想用呢啲賤招瓦解場運動<br />\n<br />\n雖然大家都知道呢啲五毛所講嘅野唔係事實只係鳩吹<br />\n但都要認真咁提防啲五毛post，因為近排大家都好關注肺炎而忽略左其他野，會比較容易被五毛分化<br />\n<br />\n大家記住近排意志要堅定，齊齊提防五毛分化技倆<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd803fe20ba07f73daeccfc7836ed83c6def6b1d","tid":1862722,"uid":239336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T19:09:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"416985ad5812df37c66a2e7d8903178af720704d","tid":1862722,"uid":146642,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T19:19:26.000Z","msg":"唔好搞咁多野啦"},{"pid":"8678bb6a2fc4fd7ae458655d3ccf57ab5c3a1b6a","tid":1862722,"uid":239336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"416985ad5812df37c66a2e7d8903178af720704d","tid":1862722,"uid":146642,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T19:19:26.000Z","msg":"唔好搞咁多野啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T19:26:05.000Z","msg":"Yes sir"},{"pid":"3598ad503e763c3c4a309b05dc9785e9e7894de7","tid":1862722,"uid":175346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T19:30:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ed2860c318de1c35fbe2e0ee7372ad6be93ed134","tid":1862722,"uid":239336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-